Name: Sparkle
Desc: A member of the Masked Fools. Inscrutable and unscrupulous.\nA dangerous maestro of theatrics, utterly engrossed in the art of performance. Adorned with innumerable masks, she is the hero with a thousand faces.\nWealth, status, power... None of this matters to Sparkle. The only thing that can get her attention is "amusement."

1.Name: Suspension of Disbelief
1.Desc: The Cipher effect applied by the Ultimate lasts for 1 extra turn. All allies affected by Cipher have their ATK increased by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>.

2.Name: Purely Fictitious
2.Desc: Each Talent stack allows allies to ignore <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> of the enemy target's DEF when dealing DMG to enemies.

3.Name: Pipedream
3.Desc: Skill Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nBasic ATK Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>10</unbreak>.

4.Name: Life Is a Gamble
4.Desc: The Ultimate recovers 1 more Skill Point. The Talent additionally increases Max Skill Points by 1.

5.Name: Parallax Truth
5.Desc: Ultimate Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nTalent Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.

6.Name: Narrative Polysemy
6.Desc: The CRIT DMG Boost effect of Sparkle's Skill additionally increases by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> of Sparkle's CRIT DMG, and her Skill's CRIT DMG Boost effect will apply to all allies currently with Cipher.

130601.Name: Monodrama
130601.Desc: Deals Quantum DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Sparkle's ATK to a single target enemy.

130602.Name: Dreamdiver
130602.Desc: Increases the CRIT DMG of a single ally by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[f1]%</unbreak></color> of Sparkle's CRIT DMG plus <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[f1]%</unbreak></color>, lasting for <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> turn(s). And at the same time, Advances Forward this ally's action by <unbreak>#4[i]%</unbreak>.\nWhen Sparkle uses this ability on herself, the Action Advance effect will not trigger.

130603.Name: The Hero with a Thousand Faces
130603.Desc: Recovers <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> Skill Points for the team and grants all allies Cipher. When allies with Cipher trigger the DMG Boost effect provided by Sparkle's Talent, each stack additionally increases its effect by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[f1]%</unbreak></color>, lasting for <unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak> turns.

130604.Name: Red Herring
130604.Desc: While Sparkle is on the battlefield, additionally increases the max number of Skill Points by <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak>. Whenever an ally consumes 1 Skill Point, all allies' DMG increases by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[f1]%</unbreak></color>. This effect lasts for <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> turn(s) and can stack up to <unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak> time(s).

130606.Name: Attack
130606.Desc: Attacks an enemy, and when the battle starts, reduces their Toughness of the corresponding Type.

130607.Name: Unreliable Narrator
130607.Desc: Using the Technique grants all allies Stealth for <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> seconds. Characters in Stealth will not be detected by enemies, and entering battle while in Stealth recovers <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Skill Point(s) for the team.

1.PointDesc: When using Basic ATK, additionally regenerates <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Energy.
The CRIT DMG Boost effect provided by the Skill lasts until the start of the target's next turn.

Increases all allies' ATK by <unbreak>#4[i]%</unbreak>. When there are 1/2/3 Quantum allies in your team, Quantum-Type allies' ATK are increased by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>/<unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>/<unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak>.
